text: "I Send a Message" is a 1984 song by Australian new wave band INXS and is the second single from their fourth studio album The Swing. The music video was filmed in Tokyo. It went to number 3 in Australia, number 18 in New Zealand and number 77 in the United States. ==Track listing== 7" single Track listing 12"/CD Maxi single Track listing == References == Category:1984 songs Category:INXS songs Category:Rock songs
